{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"594e6e6313","title":"中共中央关于党员党籍处理问题的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"194faebc2d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":12,"articleId":"594e6e6313","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"干部和干部政策","id":"3df4ae75e1","type":"主题"},{"name":"中共中央通知","id":"91736a0628","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","name":"中共党史教学参考资料 第25册 “文化大革命”参考资料 上册（1988年）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"906bb45a34","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央、国务院通告","index":0,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"149cb9199e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年二月十二日）","index":1,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"609b333410","type":"paragraph","text":"在这次无产阶级文化大革命期间，北京和各地出现了许多所谓全国性组织，它们都不是自下而上地在全国各地真正的革命派大联合的基础上，经过民主选举产生的，而是少数人临时涛合在一起组成的。其中，还有极少数组织是地、富、反、坏、右分子摘起来的。中共中央、国务院决定：","index":2,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"50200a5dc0","type":"paragraph","text":"一、所谓全国性组织、中央一律不子承认、所有这些组织应当立即取消、它们的成员应该立即从北京等地回去，到原单位参加运动。","index":3,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d300be0fc","type":"paragraph","text":"二、这些组织以各种名义宣领的公款，应一律由批款单位如数追回。在本通告下达前，已经花掉的款项必须开列清单，由批款单位进行审查，购买的实物，除已经消耗的以外，也应一律追回。本通告下达后，领到的款项，不准动用。如有携款逃置者，追查法办。","index":4,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a0df8a0e9","type":"paragraph","text":"三、这些组织，如发现有反革命活动，其成员必须向公安部门揭发报告，由公安部门负责审查处理","index":5,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1bb8c988a7","type":"paragraph","text":"特此通告。中共中央关于党员党籍处理问题的通知","index":6,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e86539303","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年二月十二日）","index":7,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"903b940631","type":"paragraph","text":"最近，有些单位的党组织或群众组织按照某些群众的要求，开除了一些党员的党籍，有的还当场烧毁了人党志愿书等档案材料。对此，中央认为","index":8,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"501baf864f","type":"paragraph","text":"、除了速捕法办的现行反革命分子应该立即开除其党籍外，一般党员的党籍处理，应该放在运动后期进行。","index":9,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"228f871c36","type":"paragraph","text":"二、按照党章规定，党员的处分，必须由党组织执行，群众及其组织，无权对党员进行党纪处分。三、有关党员的人党申请书等档案材料，不得烧毁。这个通知可以在农村、城市和部队各单位内普遍张贴。","index":10,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":307,"end":307}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"06ad58dbda","type":"paragraph","text":"各级党委、各级军区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1cd19d059f","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2fa2f594af","type":"paragraph","text":"最近，有些单位的党组织或群众组织按照某些群众的要求，开除了一些党员的党籍，有的还当场烧毁了入党志愿书等档案材料。对此，中央认为：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3d36628534","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于党员党籍处理问题的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"645d01acc2","type":"paragraph","text":"这个通知可以在农村、城市和部队各单位内普遍张贴。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"660173bc72","type":"paragraph","text":"三、有关党员的入党申请书等档案材料，不得烧毁。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67551b1b7d","type":"paragraph","text":"二、按照党章规定，党员的处分，必须由党组织执行，群众及其组织，无权对党员进行党纪处分。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d7d521321","type":"paragraph","text":"一、除了逮捕法办的现行反革命分子应该立即开除其党籍外，一般党员的党籍处理，应该放在运动后期进行。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9089ae2c37","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年二月十二日","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}